## Reports (Premium)

### What reports can I generate?

TradeFrame generates three types of PDF reports, all available from the job detail page:

1. **Photo Report** — A visual document with all job photos, including watermarked versions, GPS data, and captions. Ideal for insurance claims or client documentation.

2. **Progress Report** — A comprehensive project status document showing job details, milestone history, estimate summaries, invoice summaries, payment history, and a photo gallery.

3. **Closeout Report** — A final project summary with complete financial reconciliation (estimated vs. invoiced vs. paid vs. outstanding), a customizable thank-you message, optional customer sign-off signature, and photo gallery. Use this when handing off a completed project.

### Can I get a customer sign-off on the closeout report?

Yes. The Closeout Report view has a **Customer Sign-Off** section. The client can sign on-screen or you can photograph their signature. Their name, signature, and date are included on the final PDF.

### What do the reports look like?

Reports use a professional navy and teal color scheme with your company name, phone number, and email displayed in the header. If you've uploaded a company logo in Settings, it appears as a watermark on the report pages.

