## Calendar Integration

### How does calendar sync work?

When you create a job, TradeFrame adds an event to your default Apple Calendar with the job type, client name, address, and notes. Events are set for 2 hours with a 30-minute advance alarm. The dashboard shows a monthly calendar view with both your Apple Calendar events and TradeFrame jobs.

### Do I need to grant calendar access?

Yes. TradeFrame will ask for calendar permission on first use. If you decline, jobs won't appear on your calendar but the app still works normally. You can change this later in iOS Settings.

