## Settings

### What can I configure in Settings?

- **Business Info** — Company name, phone, email, and logo. These appear on all PDF reports.
- **Photo Settings** — Toggle watermarks on/off, adjust photo quality (50–100%), and set a default job type.
- **Notifications** — Toggle each notification type and set the payment reminder interval.
- **Subscription** — View your current plan, renewal date, restore purchases, or manage your subscription.

### How do I add my company logo?

Go to **Settings → Business Info** and tap the logo area. You can take a photo or choose from your library. The logo appears as a watermark on PDF reports. Tap the **×** button to remove it.

