## CloudKit Sync

### Does TradeFrame sync across devices?

Yes. On devices signed into iCloud, TradeFrame uses CloudKit to sync your data across all your iOS devices. Changes made on one device will appear on others. In the simulator or when iCloud is unavailable, the app falls back to local-only storage.

### Is my data backed up?

When CloudKit sync is active, your data is stored in iCloud and backed up by Apple. Local-only data (simulator or no iCloud) is only on the device and should be backed up through standard iOS device backups.

